extends layout

block content
    div.jumbotron.my-3.mx-1
        div
            h1.display-4 Welcome to RaftModding
            p.lead
                | RaftModding aims to extend the survival game Raft by adding
                |  modifications. This site provides a sorted overview over
                |  everything you need for modding your game.
        hr.my-3

        a(href='/loader').btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.mt-1 Get the mod loader
        | 
        a(href='/mods').btn.btn-outline-secondary.btn-lg.mt-1 Browse Raft Mods
    div.my-5.mx-1
        h2 What is RaftModding?
        p.text-justify RaftModding is a modding community and a ModLoader for the game #[a(href='https://raft-game.com') Raft] developed
            |  by Redbeet Interactive. Feel free to join our #[a(href='/discord') discord] to see more screenshots, or if you
            |  want to learn how to mod using our ModLoader or just to discuss.
